Skins.Name: A Step Forward
Skins.BgDescription:
A standard uniform of the Spacetrek Collective Research Institute.
Wearing it, the petite girl moves among data streams, machinery, and shifting currents. Beneath the silent gaze of the stars, humanity's drive to explore never ceases.

Skills.SkillDescribe:
Basic Attack

Perform up to 4 consecutive attacks, dealing Fusion DMG.


Heavy Attack

Consume STA to attack the target, dealing Fusion DMG.


Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode

While in Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, Basic Attack is replaced with Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode.
Perform up to 3 consecutive attacks, dealing Fusion DMG.


Mid-air Attack

Consume STA to perform Mid-air Plunging Attack, dealing Fusion DMG. Press Normal Attack within a certain time afterward to cast Basic Attack Stage 3.


Dodge Counter

Press Normal Attack right after a successful Dodge to attack the target, dealing Fusion DMG.
Press Normal Attack shortly after performing this attack to perform Basic Attack Stage 2.


Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode

While in Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, Dodge Counter is replaced with Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode.
Press Normal Attack right after a successful Dodge to counterattack and deal Fusion DMG.
Within a certain time afterward, press Normal Attack to cast Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 3.

Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 3 DMG

Skills.SkillDescribe:
Resonance Skill - Expectation Error

Heal all nearby Resonators in the team and enter the Parry state, during which DMG taken is reduced by 100% for a time. Switching to another Resonator ends this state immediately.
If attacked while in the Parry state, exit the state and cast Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution
If not attacked while in the Parry state, press Normal Attack to exit the state and cast Basic Attack Stage 2


Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution

Stagnate nearby targets and deal Fusion DMG, reducing the cooldown of Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution by 2s.
Switching to another Resonator ends the Stagnation effect early.


Resonance Skill - Distributed Array

While in Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, Resonance Skill is replaced with Resonance Skill - Distributed Array.
Heal all nearby Resonators in the team and summon Hover Cannons to strike the target, dealing Fusion DMG.
Can be performed in mid-air.

Attack all targets within the effective range, dealing Fusion DMG.
For every 1% of Mornye's Energy Regen exceeding 100%, this skill gains an additional 0.5% Crit. Rate (up to 80%) and 1% Crit. DMG (up to 160%).
When casting this skill, if a Syntony Field is present, remove it and generate a High Syntony Field.
Can be performed in mid-air.


High Syntony Field

- High Syntony Field lasts for 25s.
- Increases the DEF of all nearby Resonators in the team within the High Syntony Field by 20%.
- Inherits the Syntony Field's boost to resistance to interruption and Off-Tune Buildup Rate.
- Inherits the Syntony Field's healing effect and increases the Healing Multiplier by 40%.

Mornye's Energy Regen is increased by 10%.
Casting Intro Skill restores 20 points of Concerto Energy, triggered once every 20s.
Casting Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 3 restores 20 points of Concerto Energy, triggered once every 20s.

Casting Resonance Skill - Expectation Error or Resonance Skill - Distributed Array grants Proof of Boundedness to all Resonators in the team:
- Proof of Boundedness lasts for 60s and can be gained once every 5 min.
- When the active Resonator takes DMG greater than 30% of their Max HP, they instead take DMG equal to 30% of their Max HP. This effect can trigger up to 3 times. Proof of Boundedness is removed after triggering it 3 times.
- When the active Resonator takes a fatal blow, they are not downed by this instance of damage. This effect can trigger up to 1 times. Proof of Boundedness is removed after triggering it 1 times.
- When Proof of Boundedness is removed, the active Resonator restores HP equal to 150% of Mornye's DEF.
Attack the target to deal Fusion DMG, clearing all Rest Mass Energy and entering Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode.

Baseline Mode

While in her default Baseline Mode, Mornye gains Rest Mass Energy.


Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift

When Rest Mass Energy reaches 100 points, Heavy Attack is replaced with Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift.
Cast Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift to deal Fusion DMG, considered Heavy Attack DMG. Afterward, Mornye jumps into mid-air, consumes all Rest Mass Energy and enter Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode.


Wide Field Observation Mode

Wide Field Observation Mode last for 30s.
- Upon entering Wide Field Observation Mode, Mornye generates a Syntony Field.
- While in Wide Field Observation Mode, Mornye gains Relative Momentum.
- If Relative Momentum is below 100 when holding Normal Attack, perform Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode Stage 1 to 3 in sequence. If Relative Momentum reaches 100 during this time, cast Heavy Attack - Inversion instead.
- While moving, Mornye continuously consumes STA. STA cannot be recovered while in Wide Field Observation Mode Stage.
- When Dodging with directional input, Mornye starts to fly at speed, which lasts for up to 10s or until STA is depleted or until the Wide Field Observation Mode ends.
- When Mornye is hit or launched into mid-air, press Dodge to immediately recover from the attack. This effect can be triggered up to 3 times, which resets when Wide Field Observation Mode ends.
- Press Jump and Mornye will slowly descend, before she lands, Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode, Resonance Skill - Distributed Array, and Heavy Attack - Inversion are unavailable.
Performing environmental interactions, using Utilities, or switching to another Resonator ends Wide Field Observation Mode. The state also ends when Mornye is no longer airborne.


Syntony Field

- Syntony Field lasts for 25s.
- When the Syntony Field is generated, deal Fusion DMG, considered Resonance Liberation DMG.
- Continuously restores HP for all nearby Resonators in the team within the Syntony Field, triggered once every 3s.
- Increases the Off-Tune Buildup Rate of all nearby Resonators in the team within the Syntony Field by 50%.
- Enhances the resistance to interruption of all nearby Resonators in the team within the Syntony Field.


Heavy Attack - Inversion

- When Relative Momentum reaches 100 points, Heavy Attack is replaced with Heavy Attack - Inversion.
- Consume all Relative Momentum to cast Heavy Attack - Inversion, dealing Fusion DMG, considered Heavy Attack DMG.
- Heavy Attack - Inversion inflicts Observation Marker upon the target on hit for 30s.


Observation Marker

When a Resonator in the team deals Tune Break DMG to a target inflicted with Observation Marker, Mornye inflicts an Interfered Marker on the target for 8s.


Interfered Marker

Targets affected by Tune Rupture - Interfered or Tune Strain - Interfered take increased DMG from all nearby Resonators in the team. For every 1% of Mornye's Energy Regen exceeding 100%, their DMG is increased by 0.25%, up to 40%.


Visual Field

When a Resonator in the team defeats a target inflicted with Observation Marker or Interfered Marker, Mornye gains Visual Field for 3s. While in this state, Mornye inflicts Observation Marker on the target hit whenever any Resonator in the team deals damage.


Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet

Mornye deals one instance of Fusion DMG to a targets in the Tune Rupture - Interfered state within range, considered Tune Rupture DMG.


Rest Mass Energy

Mornye can hold up to 100 points of Rest Mass Energy.
While in Baseline Mode, she gains Rest Mass Energy when performing Basic Attack, Heavy Attack, Dodge Counter, or when Resonance Skill - Optimal Solution hits a target.


Relative Momentum

Mornye can hold up to 100 points of Relative Momentum.
While in Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, she gains Relative Momentum when Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode, Dodge Counter - Wide Field Observation Mode or Resonance Skill - Distributed Array hits the target.
Mornye cannot gain Relative Momentum during Heavy Attack - Inversion.

Skills.SkillDescribe: Has a chance to produce special dishes when cooking.
All Resonators in the team gain 25% All-Type DMG Amplification for 30s.

Mornye can respond to Tune Rupture - Interfered and Tune Strain - Interfered.
Responding to Tune Rupture - Interfered: When the active Resonator deals damage to a target affected by Tune Rupture - Interfered, Mornye casts Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jet. Each target can be damaged by this skill up to once every 8s.
Responding to Tune Strain - Interfered: Each stack of Tune Strain - Interfered on the target increases Mornye's total DMG against them. Every point of Mornye's Tune Break Boost increases the total DMG by 0.12%. While Mornye is in the team, the max stack limit of Tune Strain - Interfered on a target is increased by 1.
Mornye can perform Tune Break against the targets with full Off-Tune Level.

ResonantChain.AttributesDescription:
Basic Attack Wide Field Observation Mode becomes immune to interruption.
Mornye can now inflict Interfered Marker even when the target is not affected by Tune Rupture - Interfered or Tune Strain - Interfered. Interfered Marker's duration is extended by 150%s.
When Mornye applies Observation Marker on a target, she also inflicts Interfered Marker.

All nearby Resonators in the team gain Crit. DMG increase against targets with Interfered Marker: Every 1% of Mornye's Energy Regen over 100% grants 0.2% Crit. DMG increase, up to 32%.
Syntony Field and High Syntony Field further increase the Off-Tune Buildup Rate of all Resonators in the team by 20%.
Casting Resonance Skill - Distributed Array additionally restores 25 points of Concerto Energy and all Relative Momentum, triggered once every 25s.
The healing of High Syntony Field is increased by 30%.

The DMG Multiplier of Resonance Liberation - Critical Protocol is increased by 40%.
The DMG Multiplier of Tune Rupture Response - Particle Jetis increased by 160%.

ResonantChain.NodeName: To the Far Shores of the Stars
ResonantChain.AttributesDescription: Resonance Liberation - Critical Protocol deals 400% more DMG. If Mornye has not engaged in combat for over 4s, she restores Resonance Energy equal to 10% of her Max Resonance Energy every 0.2s.

SkillDescList: Generate a Syntony Field that restores HP and increases Off-Tune Buildup Rate.
Inflict Interfered Marker that increases the DMG the target takes.
Outro Skill grants All-Type DMG Amplification to all Resonators in the team.
DescList: Basic Attack resotres Relative Momentum on hit.
While in Wide Field Observation Mode, Basic Attack and Resonance Skill restores Relative Momentum on hit.

InputDetails.description: While in Baseline Mode, press + + to gain Rest Mass Energy.
Heavy Attack - Geopotential Shift: When Rest Mass Energy is full, hold to enter Wide Field Observation Mode to provide buffs to Resonators in the team.
Basic Attack - Wide Field Observation Mode: While in Wide Field Observation Mode, press + + to gain Relative Momentum.
Heavy Attack - Inversion: When Relative Momentum is full, hold to increase the DMG dealt to the target.
Resonance Liberation - Critical Protocol: press to cast this skill.
